name: TableDefault

<twig:Table>

    <twig:Table:TableHeader>
        <twig:Table:TableRow>
            <twig:Table:TableHead className="w-[100px]">Invoice</twig:Table:TableHead>

            <twig:Table:TableHead className="text-right">Amount</twig:Table:TableHead>

    </twig:Table:TableHeader>
    <twig:Table:TableBody>
        <twig:Table:TableRow>
            <twig:Table:TableCell className="font-medium">INV001</twig:Table:TableCell>

            <twig:Table:TableCell>Credit Card</twig:Table:TableCell>

        </twig:Table:TableRow>
    </twig:Table:TableBody>
